Name: Chicago Fire
Title: Danger Is All Around
Desc: A familiar face returns to Firehouse 51 to serve with Kidd on a special task force.
LongDescription: A familiar face returns to Firehouse 51 to serve with Kidd on a special task force; with Tony close to breaking the CFD's perfect attendance record, Mouch and Capp work to keep him safe; old grudges resurface when Gallo reunites with a family member.
